JDocFile/KSHM/111%2c%e8%81%b2%2c849%2c20220729%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"KSHM,111,聲,849,20220729,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"聲","JNO":"849","JDATE":"20220729","JTITLE":"聲請定其應執行刑"}